    "body": "I noticed that we're unnecessarily re-creating the sampling metadata twice when reordering the batch requests into prefill and decode groups for MLA.\n\nThis moves the reorder op from the start of the `_prepare_inputs()` method to the end of the `_update_stats()` method (which is called right before).",
